data.description: Beautiful one story home that features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with an additional living space that can be used as a game room, living room or office/study. New HVAC system and the Roof is 4 years old. Wood and Ceramic tile floors throughout the home. Upon entry of the home you have an open foyer that leads to the Living Room. The living area opens up to the dining and kitchen area. The kitchen features granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances. The second living area features book shelves and an electric fire place making it great for those cold Texas winters. Off the hallway you have the first two spacious secondary bedrooms and a full bath. The Primary bedroom has wood floors, ceiling fan and a sliding barn door that leads to the primary bathroom. The primary bath has a single vanity with an oversized walk in shower and a makeup vanity. The laundry room is tucked away in the hallway off the kitchen and back porch area making it great for rainy days. Large covered patio that leads to the huge gorgeous backyard great for summer BBQs. The backyard features a new fence and a concrete/stone fire pit. 2 car garage with additional storage space and is pre-plumbed for a water softener.  NO HOA!! This home feeds to the NEISD School District and is conveniently located close to Olmos Basin Golf Course, tons of shopping and dining and entertainment!!
